				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Definitely get the cc65 package and start with that. It contains a very powerful macro assembler (ca65) that compiles to object files, and has a linker (ld65). The package also contains a C compiler that you can start using once you get your feet wet.<br /><br />Shiru's article linked above is an excellent starting point if you already know C.</div>

