					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It is supposed to compile only when you use the files provided along the examples, i.e. changing the CFG file without considering underlying code requriements may introduce problems.<br /><br />It should comiple as provided with the v2.13.3, at least it does compile properly for me. I.e. I downloaded <a href="http://shiru.untergrund.net/files/src/cc65_nes_examples.zip" class="postlink">the examples archive</a> and compiled it successfully without any changes and any extra actions with the specified version of CC65 package. If it does not compile properly, my only guess is that you have some other (newer) version that introduced some incompatibility.</div>

