						<div class="postbody">Shiru, the first line of your bat file doesn't work correctly:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">path=path;..\bin\</div><br />This will set the path to, literally, &quot;path;..\bin\&quot;. It should be:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">path=%path%;..\bin\</div><br />This is unrelated to any CC65 problems.</div>

					
